s</a>			</span>
									<span class="sep"> | </span>
							<span class="tag-links">
				<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-tag-links">Tagged</span> <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/acta" rel="tag">ACTA</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/activism" rel="tag">activism</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/assassination" rel="tag">assassination</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/doctorow" rel="tag">Doctorow</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/extremism" rel="tag">extremism</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/intelligence-2" rel="tag">intelligence</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/machon" rel="tag">Machon</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/sopa" rel="tag">SOPA</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/spies-2" rel="tag">spies</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/surveillance-2" rel="tag">surveillance</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/terrorism-2" rel="tag">terrorism</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/torture-2" rel="tag">torture</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/tag/wikileaks" rel="tag">Wikileaks</a>			</span>
						
					</footer><!-- #entry-meta -->
	</article><!-- #post-11 -->

				
					
