						<div class="entry-meta">
				<span class="sep">Posted on </span><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2011/09/libya-mi6-and-torture-interview-on-press-tv-2.html" title="21:05" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2011-09-22T21:05:34+00:00" pubdate>September 22, 2011</time></a><span class="by-author"> <span class="sep"> by </span> <span class="author vcard"><span class="byauthor">Annie Machon</span></span></span><br>
                                <a href="#" onclick="javascript:copyToClipboard('http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2011/09/libya-mi6-and-torture-interview-on-press-tv-2.html')">Copy permalink to clipboard</a>
                                <br>			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
			
		</header><!-- .entry-header -->

				<div class="entry-content">
			<p>Libya, <span class="caps">MI6</span>, tor­ture, and more happy sub­jects dis­cussed recently on “Africa Today” on Press <span class="caps">TV</span>. </p>
<p>The pro­gramme was inter­est­ing, informed and bal­anced.  Do have a watch:</p>
<p><iframe src="http://player.vimeo.com/video/29444484" frameborder="0" height="224" width="320"></iframe></p>
