	<article id="post-110" class="post-110 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-current-affairs category-democracy category-gaddafi category-intelligence category-interviews category-libya category-machon category-mi6 category-rttv category-spies category-terrorism category-tv tag-gaddafi tag-intelligence-2 tag-libya tag-lockerbie tag-machon tag-mi6 tag-spies-2 tag-terrorism-2">
		<header class="entry-header">
						<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2011/02/libya-interview-rttv-23-february-2011.html" title="Permalink to Libya Interview, RTTV 23 February 2011" rel="bookmark">Libya Interview, <span class="caps">RTTV</span> 23 February 2011</a></h1>
			
						<div class="entry-meta">
				<span class="sep">Posted on </span><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2011/02/libya-interview-rttv-23-february-2011.html" title="14:55" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2011-02-24T14:55:21+00:00" pubdate>February 24, 2011</time></a><span class="by-author"> <span class="sep"> by </span> <span class="author vcard"><span class="byauthor">Annie Machon</span></span></span><br>
                                <a href="#" onclick="javascript:copyToClipboard('http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2011/02/libya-interview-rttv-23-february-2011.html')">Copy permalink to clipboard</a>
                                <br>			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
			
		</header><!-- .entry-header -->

				<div class="entry-content">
			<p>My inter­view for <span class="caps">RTTV</span> about the cur­rent Libyan crisis:</p>
<p><iframe frameborder="0" height="360" src="http://player.vimeo.com/video/20295961" width="488"></iframe> </p>
					</div><!-- .entry-content -->
		
		<footer class="entry-meta">
                        <a href="#" onclick="javascript:copyToClipboard('http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2011/02/libya-interview-rttv-23-february-2011.html')">Copy permalink to clipboard</a> &#8195;| &#8195;<a href="http://anniemachon.ch/privacy">Why no sharings links?</a><br>
												<span class="cat-links">
				<span class="entry-utility-prep entry-utility-prep-cat-links">Posted in</span> <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/current-affairs" title="View all posts in Current Affairs" rel="category tag">Current Affairs</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/democracy" title="View all posts in Democracy" rel="category tag">Democracy</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/gaddafi" title="View all posts in Gaddafi" rel="category tag">Gaddafi</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/intelligence" title="View all posts in Intelligence" rel="category tag">Intelligence</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/interviews" title="View all posts in Interviews" rel="category tag">Interviews</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/libya" title="View all posts in Libya" rel="category tag">Libya</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/machon" title="View all posts in Machon" rel="category tag">Machon</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/mi6" title="View all posts in MI6" rel="category tag">MI6</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/rttv" title="View all posts in RTTV" rel="category tag">RTTV</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/spies" title="View all posts in Spies" rel="category tag">Spies</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/terrorism" title="View all posts in Terrorism" rel="category tag">Terrorism</a>, <a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/category/tv" title="View all posts in TV" rel="category tag">TV</a>			</span>
